data.description: WELCOME TO A VERY DESIRABLE RANCH-STYLE HOME IN THE HEART OF JUSTICE. THIS BEAUTIFUL AND METICULOUSLY MAINTAINED HOME NESTLED ON A PICTURESQUE CORNER LOT IS WAITING FOR YOU TO CALL IT HOME! THE LIVING SPACES ARE LIGHT-FILLED AND INVITING. YOU WILL LOVE TO GATHER WITH GUESTS IN THE DINING AREA WHILE THOSE WHO LOVE TO COOK WILL APPRECIATE THE KITCHEN WITH PLENTY OF COUNTER SPACE, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, AND EAT-IN-KITCHEN SPACE. THREE GOOD SIZE BEDROOMS, HARDWOOD FLOORS THROUGH, AND MANY RECENT INTERIOR AND EXTERIOR UPDATES INCLUDING A NEW A/C, HOT WATER TANK, WINDOWS, WASHER/DRYER, AND MORE. PLENTY OF OUTSIDE SPACE TO ENTERTAIN. CONVENIENTLY LOCATED JUST MINUTES FROM SHOPPING, DINING, AND EXPRESSWAY ACCESS. JUST A BLOCK AWAY FROM THE PARK/GOTTWALD PLAYGROUND. YOU DON'T WANT TO MISS THIS EXTRAORDINARY OPPORTUNITY.
